msgid ""
"Enable sending of keep-alive messages on connection-oriented sockets.  "
"Expects an integer boolean flag."
msgstr ""
"Active l'émission de messages périodiques gardant la socket ouverte pour les "
"sockets orientées connexion. Demande un attribut entier booléen."

#. type: TP
#: archlinux debian-buster debian-unstable mageia-cauldron
#, no-wrap
msgid "B<SO_LINGER>"
msgstr "B<SO_LINGER>"

#. type: Plain text
#: archlinux debian-buster debian-unstable mageia-cauldron
msgid ""
"Sets or gets the B<SO_LINGER> option.  The argument is a I<linger> structure."
msgstr ""
"Définit ou lit l'option B<SO_LINGER>. Le paramètre est une structure "
"I<linger>."

#. type: Plain text
#: archlinux debian-buster debian-unstable mageia-cauldron
#, no-wrap
msgid ""
"struct linger {\n"
